n43\t# or in workspace:\n44\tgit clone https://github.com/samber/cc-skills-golang.git ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/cc-skills-golang\n45\t```\n46\t\n47\t</details>\n48\t\n49\t<details>\n50\t<summary>Gemini CLI</summary>\n51\t\n52\t```bash\n53\tgemini extensions install https://github.com/samber/cc-skills-golang\n54\t```\n55\t\n56\tUpdate with `gemini extensions update cc-skills-golang`.\n57\t\n58\t</details>\n59\t\n60\t<details>\n61\t<summary>Cursor</summary>\n62\t\n63\tCopy skills into the cross-client discovery directory:\n64\t\n65\t```bash\n66\tgit clone https://github.com/samber/cc-skills-golang.git  ~/.cursor/skills/cc-skills-golang\n67\t```\n68\t\n69\tCursor auto-discovers skills from `.agents/skills/` and `.cursor/skills/`.\n70\t\n71\t</details>\n72\t\n73\t<details>\n74\t<summary>Copilot</summary>\n75\t\n76\tCopy skills into the cross-client discovery directory:\n77\t\n78\t```bash\n79\t/plugin install https://github.com/samber/cc-skills-golang\n80\t# or\n81\tgit clone https://github.com/samber/cc-skills-golang.git ~/.copilot/skills/cc-skills-golang\n82\t```\n83\t\n84\tCopilot auto-discovers skills from `.copilot/skills/`.\n85\t\n86\t</details>\n87\t\n88\t<details>\n89\t<summary>OpenCode</summary>\n90\t\n91\tCopy skills into the cross-client discovery directory:\n92\t\n93\t```bash\n94\tgit clone https://github.com/samber/cc-skills-golang.git ~/.agents/skills/cc-skills-golang\n95\t```\n96\t\n97\tOpenCode auto-discovers skills from `.agents/skills/`, `.opencode/skills/`, and `.claude/skills/`.\n98\t\n99\t</details>\n100\t\n101\t<details>\n102\t<summary>Codex (OpenAI)</summary>\n103\t\n104\tClone into the cross-client discovery path:\n105\t\n106\t```bash\n107\tgit clone https://github.com/samber/cc-skills-golang.git ~/.agents/skills/cc-skills-golang\n108\t```\n109\t\n110\tCodex auto-discovers skills from `~/.agents/skills/` and `.agents/skills/`. Update with `cd ~/.agents/skills/cc-skills-golang && git pull`.\n111\t\n112\t</details>\n113\t\n114\t<details>\n115\t<s