ary>OpenCode</summary>\n\nAdd to your OpenCode config:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"plugin\": [\"skills@git+https://github.com/entireio/skills.git\"]\n}\n```\n\nOpenCode auto-registers the skills directory via `.opencode/plugins/entire.js`. See [`.opencode/INSTALL.md`](.opencode/INSTALL.md) for details.\n\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Codex (OpenAI)</summary>\n\nClone into the cross-client discovery path:\n\n```bash\ngit clone https://github.com/entireio/skills.git ~/.agents/skills/entire\n```\n\nCodex auto-discovers skills from `~/.agents/skills/` and `.agents/skills/`. Update with `cd ~/.agents/skills/entire && git pull`.\n\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Copilot</summary>\n\n```bash\n/plugin install https://github.com/entireio/skills\n# or\ngit clone https://github.com/entireio/skills.git ~/.copilot/skills/entire\n```\n\nCopilot auto-discovers skills from `.copilot/skills/`.\n\n</details>\n\n<!-- prettier-ignore-end -->"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":224,"cache_read_input_tokens":65106,"output_tokens":1207,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":224,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":1207,"cache_read_input_tokens":65106,"cache_creation_input_tokens":224,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":224},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CaNwm5MJn12B2LComfq95","type":"assistant","uuid":"91484ca2-195b-4c7a-a3d4-eb59a251f011","timestamp":"2026-04-24T16:53:58.063Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/alisha/Projects/skills","sessionId":"95047199-69f0-49a5-9432-18cba428ecec","version":"2.1.119","gitBranch":"alisha/refactor","slug":"eventual-jumping-sutherland"}
